Notes: Stephanie Cleary tied the game with two free throws with 22 seconds left but
Rochester held the Bombers to one basket over a 10-minute span during the
second half and overtime. Ithaca, ranked sixth in the NCAA East Region, plays
at Alfred Friday and at St. John Fisher Saturday.
Game.Officials: Steve Berwind,  Peter Sielaff,  Owen Smith
